<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hap1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hap,</orth> subst. fortune: <cit><quote>had not our h. been bad,</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 1.1.39" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 1, 39</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>whom it was their h. to save,</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 1.1.39" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 1, 39</bibl></cit> <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.269" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 2, 269</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.314" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 314</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.3.8" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 3, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.3.8" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 3, 8</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tit 5.2.101" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. V, 2, 101</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 2.3.32" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 3, 32</bibl>. <cit><quote>blessed h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.6.10" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 6, 10</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>contented h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.84" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 84</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>my dear h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 2.2.190" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 2, 190</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>golden h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 42" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 42</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>good h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.1.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. I, 1, 15</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.1.23" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 1, 23</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.3.171" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 3, 171</bibl>. <cit><quote>by good h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 2.210" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL II, 210</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tim 3.2.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. III, 2, 27</bibl>. <cit><quote>direful h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.17" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 17</bibl></cit>. <emph>ill h.</emph> H8 Epil. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.17" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 17</bibl> Plur. <emph>--s</emph>: <cit><quote>loving goes by --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 3.1.105" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 1, 105</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>our heavy --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 5.3.202" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. V, 3, 202</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>howe'er my --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.3.70" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 3, 70</bibl></cit>.
